{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2504035, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "国外的资源好很多，看看美国有哈佛，MIT，stanford，加州理工等十几所名校，美国人还比中国人少很多很多。美国人均机会真的比国内大的多，国内不值得。", "timestamp": 1631598810, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504042, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "家里没米", "timestamp": 1631598874, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504046, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "国内卷半天，保上你清研了，课题组导师水平不行的也有很多很多，拉跨学不到东西", "timestamp": 1631598917, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504066, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": 2504046, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 大实话", "timestamp": 1631599170, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504077, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "申不到好学校sos", "timestamp": 1631599292, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504094, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": 2504077, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 美前五十就挺好的，申个好专业，现在新绩点还是情况好了很多", "timestamp": 1631599504, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504106, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": 2504042, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 国外可以考虑德国等消费学费很低的地方（教学好），另外香港三校也可以考虑。都比你清性价比高。 当然国内中科院强所的好的课题组也很好", "timestamp": 1631599672, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2504109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": 2504042, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 德国英授项目不错", "timestamp": 1631599697, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2508141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 477922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没钱qaq", "timestamp": 1631632248, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 13, "pid": 477922, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "个人感觉这年头清华的大家能出国还是出国吧，清本保研越来越难，不划算，大家实际都很优秀，现在的大部分导师们要不就是当年读本校博士，毕业直接留校（当年很简单），要不就是去国外读了博。当年他们大四毕业实际水准和我们半斤八两，甚至还没我们强，没必要内卷保研留不下被他们嫌弃或冷嘲热讽。", "timestamp": 1631598625, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631632247, "url": "", "vote": {}}}